-How many billing alarms do you get for free?
In Amazon Free Tier account, it gives 1o free billing alarms. 

-When a billing alarm is triggered how will you know?
In Amazon Free Tier account, it has SNS simple notification service.
It more depends on how it is configured for example is it set for sending email when threshold achive or by SNS.
It can be monitored in CloudWatch dashboard in AWS console.

-What is the difference between a billing alarm and a cloudwatch alarm?
Billing Alarm
  * Monitors AWS spending and triggers SNS/email on billing threshold reached
  * Focused on cost management.
CloudWatch Alarm 
  * Monitors Various AWS resources for example EC2, it CPU usage and Disk metrics
  * Alert based on how much resource is used and health metrics


aws cloudwatch describe-alarms --alarm-names "Billing-Alarm-5"
